Class SiriusIonAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.msdk.datamodel.SimpleIonAnnotation

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IonAnnotation

    public class SiriusIonAnnotation
extends SimpleIonAnnotation

    Class SiriusIonAnnotation

    This class extends SimpleIonAnnotation and adds several fields FTree - the result tree provided by Sirius experiment processed SMILES - the result string provided by FingerIdWebMethod, after computation of FingerprintCandidates DBLinks - map of DB name->id, shows where corresponding result element can be found (ex.: Pubchem: 3123) Score fields - score value from Sirius result or FingerId result objects
